Uses of Package
org.vngx.jsch.cipher

  • Packages that use org.vngx.jsch.cipher 
    Package Description
    org.vngx.jsch.cipher  
  • Classes in org.vngx.jsch.cipher used by org.vngx.jsch.cipher 
    Class and Description
    Cipher
    Cipher defines an interface for an algorithm for performing encryption or decryption.
    CipherException
    Implementation of JSchException for errors relating to the usage of Cipher instances.
    CipherImpl
    Implementation of Cipher which wraps a javax.crypto.Cipher instance from Java's JCE.
    CipherImpl.ARCFOUR
    Implementation of Cipher for arcfour (RC4) cipher.
    CipherImpl.ARCFOUR128
    Implementation of Cipher for arcfour-128 cipher.
    CipherImpl.TripleDESCBC
    Implementation of Cipher for 3des-cbc cipher.
    CipherManager
    Manager for maintaining the AlgorithmFactory instance used to create instances of Cipher.
